tinuously improving our operational effectiveness through a committed team of executive members who meet frequently to evaluate and improve our programs. This proactive leadership ensures that Saksham Bharti remains a dynamic and responsive organization, ready to meet the changing needs of the community.\n\nLooking ahead, our vision is to create a prosperous, value-based, and inclusive society where opportunities are available to the last man in the row. We aim to expand our reach further, embracing new technologies and partnerships to enhance our impact. As we celebrate our Silver Jubilee, we renew our commitment to service and excellence. We invite everyone to join us in this transformative journey—whether as a supporter, volunteer, or well-wisher. Together, we can build a future where every individual has the chance to grow, contribute, and thrive, continuing the legacy of Saksham Bharti for many more years to come. We believe that with every course completed and every learner empowered, we take another step toward a more skilled and harmonious society.','frontend/assets/images/blog_silver_jubilee.png','2026-05-14 09:34:02'),(2,'Swami Vivekanand Ajeevika Mahotsav: Record-Breaking Results','The Swami Vivekanand Ajeevika Mahotsav, Saksham Bharti\'s signature mega job fair, reached new heights this year. Organized with the primary objective of bridging the gap between employers and job seekers from marginalized communities, the event has become a beacon of hope for many. Held at the prestigious Bhaskaracharya College of Applied Sciences in Dwarka, the fair witnessed an unprecedented turnout. The energy was palpable as hundreds of trained and eager candidates gathered to showcase their skills to potential employers, marking a significant milestone in our livelihood support initiatives.\n\nThis year\'s Mahotsav was characterized by the participation of 27 prominent companies from diverse sectors, including BPO, Retail, Finance & Accounts, Sales & Marketing, and Healthcare. Renowned organizations such as LIC India, PNB Kitchenmate, and Adisports India were among the employers seeking talent. This diversity of sectors ensured that our trainees from various backgrounds—be it IT, Beauty Culture, or Fashion Designing—had multiple opportunities to find roles that matched their training and aspirations. The presence of such esteemed partners underscores the industry\'s recognition of the quality of training provided at Saksham Bharti.\n\nAs part of the preparations for the Mahotsav, our outreach team visited and interacted with several participating companies across different sectors. The purpose of these visits was to understand their specific hiring needs, explore opportunities for long-term collaboration, and ensure a perfect alignment between trainee skills and employer requirements. These interactions provided us with valuable insights into the job roles in demand, such as customer support, sales executives, accounting associates, and logistics staff. This proactive engagement ensures that our training remains directly linked to actual job market opportunities.\n\nThe statistics from the event are truly impressive and reflect the hard work of both our staff and trainees. Over 744 interviews were conducted throughout the day, providing candidates with invaluable real-world exposure to recruitment processes. Out of 308 candidates who participated in this specific mega fair, many received on-the-spot offers or were shortlisted for further rounds. When combined with our quarterly placement drives across all centers, a total of 390 candidates secured job placements in the reporting year alone. These numbers are more than just data; they represent 390 individuals who now have a steady income and a path to financial independence.\n\nA key factor in the success of the Job Fair is the rigorous pre-counselling sessions conducted by Saksham Bharti in collaboration with partners like NIIT Foundation and GTT. These sessions were designed to prepare trainees for the demands of the job market, focusing on resume building, interview techniques, and professional etiquette. By the time the candidates reached the fair, they were not just skilled in their respective trades but also confident in their ability to communicate their value to employers. This holistic preparation is what gives our trainees an edge and ensures high selection rates.\n\nIn addition to technical skills, we place a strong emphasis on soft skills and emotional intelligence. Our training includes sessions on teamwork, time management, workplace ethics, and grooming standards. We believe that these \'life skills\' are just as important as technical proficiency for long-term career success. By equipping our youth with these essential tools, we ensure they are not just job-ready but also career-ready. The positive feedback we receive from employers about the professional conduct of our graduates is a testament to the effectiveness of this holistic approach.\n\nThe impact of the Ajeevika Mahotsav extends beyond the immediate job offers. It provides a platform for industry-academia linkage, allowing our team to interact with HR representatives and understand the evolving needs of the job market. This feedback is crucial for us to refine our curriculum and ensure our training remains market-relevant. Moreover, for many candidates, even if they were not selected this time, the experience of facing multiple interviews and receiving feedback is a transformative learning opportunity that builds their resilience and prepares them for future endeavors.\n\nAs we look to the future, we aim to scale the Swami Vivekanand Ajeevika Mahotsav to even greater heights. We want to bring in more companies and offer a wider range of job roles to our trainees. The success of this year\'s event has motivated us to continue our efforts with even more vigor. We believe that by creating these direct links between skill development and employment, we are tackling the root cause of poverty and inequality. The Mahotsav is not just a one-day event; it is the culmination of months of hard work and the beginning of a new chapter for hundreds of young men and women who are now ready to contribute to the nation\'s economy. Every successful placement is a step toward a more prosperous and inclusive society.','frontend/assets/images/blog_job_fair.png','2026-05-14 09:34:02'),(3,'Empowering Academic Excellence: The Uthaan Scholarship','At Saksham Bharti, we believe that financial constraints should never be a barrier to academic excellence. Our \'Uthaan\' Scholarship Program was established with the specific goal of supporting bright and deserving trainees who aspire to pursue higher education. Many of our students have the potential and the drive to succeed in university-level studies but lack the resources to do so. Uthaan provides them with the necessary financial support and encouragement to continue their educational journey, ensuring that their dreams of a professional career can become a reality. This initiative is a cornerstone of our efforts to promote social mobility.\n\nThe scholarship selection process is rigorous and transparent, designed to identify candidates who demonstrate both academic merit and genuine financial need. Each year, we conduct annual scholarship interviews from June to September, where a panel of experts evaluates students based on their academic records, leadership potential, and commitment to social change. These interactions are more than just interviews; they are a platform for students to share their aspirations and receive guidance from experienced professionals. This year, we conducted interviews across all our centers, ensuring that every eligible student had the opportunity to apply for this life-changing support and showcase their potential.\n\nThe impact of the Uthaan program is reflected in the numbers and the stories of the recipients. In the 2024-25 reporting year, 345 students were selected for scholarships across our locations, including Raghubir Nagar, Dwarka, Vikas Nagar, and even our outreach programs in Nangloi and Amroha. The scholarship amounts are transferred directly to the students\' bank accounts after their admission to college is confirmed, ensuring a seamless and efficient process. This financial aid covers tuition fees and other critical educational expenses, significantly reducing the burden on the students and their families, and allowing them to focus entirely on their academic pursuits.\n\nOne of the unique aspects of our support is the Post Training Support Program, which assists trainees after they complete their vocational courses. This includes guidance for examinations like CUET, which is essential for admission to prestigious universities. We believe that our responsibility doesn\'t end with a certificate; it continues until our students are successfully integrated into their next phase of growth. Whether it is higher education or employment, we provide the necessary hand-holding to ensure they don\'t face these transitions alone. This comprehensive support system is what makes Saksham Bharti a true partner in our students\' success.\n\nThe stories of our scholarship recipients are truly inspiring and serve as a testament to the program\'s effectiveness. We have students who are now pursuing degrees in engineering, commerce, information technology, and the arts—fields they once thought were completely out of reach. These young men and women are not just achieving personal success; they are becoming role models in their communities, proving that with hard work and the right support, anything is possible. The scholarship program also encourages a culture of excellence within our training centers, as students are motivated to perform their best to qualify for this prestigious award.\n\nBeyond the financial support, the Uthaan program provides students with a sense of recognition and validation. Being selected for the scholarship is an acknowledgment of their hard work and potential, which significantly boosts their self-esteem and confidence. We also maintain a relationship with our scholars, providing them with continued mentorship and career counseling as they navigate their higher education. This holistic support ensures that they not only enter university but also thrive and successfully graduate, ready to take on professional roles in the workforce and give back to society.\n\nFurthermore, we organize inspirational visits by distinguished achievers to motivate our students. For instance, hosting Riya Saini, who secured a high rank in the UPSC examination, provided our students with a powerful example of what can be achieved through dedication. Such interactions allow students to learn from the experiences of others and gain valuable insights for their own academic and professional journeys. Her presence was a motivating factor, encouraging them to work towards their aspirations with renewed energy. At Saksham Bharti, we believe that exposure to success is as important as the resources to achieve it.\n\nAs we look ahead, our goal is to grow the Uthaan Scholarship Program even further. We want to increase the number of scholarships we offer and reach more students in need across a wider geographical area. We also aim to establish partnerships with more educational institutions and corporate sponsors to provide our scholars with even more opportunities for internships and placements. The success of Uthaan is a testament to the power of collective effort, and we invite our supporters to contribute to this cause. By investing in the education of these bright young minds, we are investing in the future of our nation, one scholar at a time, and creating a more equitable society.','frontend/assets/images/blog_scholarship.png','2026-05-14 09:34:02'),(4,'Ulaas Camps & Community Outreach: Fostering Creative Growth','Community outreach has always been a core pillar of Saksham Bharti\'s mission. We believe that for a society to truly prosper, empowerment must begin at the grassroots level. This year, our outreach efforts were headlined by \'Ulaas: Summer Camps\', a vibrant initiative that brought joy and learning to over 450 children across all our centers. For one week in May, our facilities were transformed into hubs of creativity, where children from nearby communities participated in various activities designed to nurture their artistic and personal growth, reinforcing our commitment to holistic development and community wellbeing.\n\nThe Ulaas Summer Camps featured a diverse range of activities, from yoga and meditation for physical and mental wellness to energetic Zumba classes and dance sessions. Children also engaged in singing, art, and craft workshops, where they were encouraged to express their imagination freely. These activities were not just about fun; they were carefully designed to build confidence, teamwork, and social skills in a supportive environment. The grand finale of the camp was a colorful event where children proudly performed and showcased their creations to their families and our volunteers, creating memories that will last a lifetime and strengthening the bond between Saksham Bharti and the communities we serve.\n\nIn addition to the summer camps, our community engagement was further enriched by the Annual Drawing Competition held in February. This event was simultaneously conducted at multiple venues, including schools, NGOs, and residential societies, ensuring wide participation across different age groups. The competition encouraged youth to showcase their artistic talents through theme-based creativity, often focusing on social and cultural themes. Recognition and awards, including certificates and prizes, were given to outstanding participants, providing them with a sense of achievement and encouraging them to continue pursuing their creative interests and self-expression.\n\nAnother significant highlight of our outreach program was the specialized Bridal Makeup Inter-center Competition. This event provided a platform for our Beauty Culture trainees to showcase their professional skills in a competitive yet encouraging setting. Participants transformed models into elegant brides using a variety of traditional and contemporary styles, incorporating unique color combinations and artistic flair. Evaluated by a panel of experts, the competition simulated a real-world work environment, preparing our trainees for the high standards and creative demands of the bridal beauty industry. Such events are crucial for building the professional confidence and portfolio of our students.\n\nOur commitment to the community also extends to providing critical health and wellness services. In collaboration with Aakash Healthcare, we organized a free Health Check-up Camp that provided essential medical services to trainees, staff, and local residents. The services included general health screenings, BMI checks, and consultations with specialists like physicians and dieticians. Preventive health advice on nutrition, exercise, and lifestyle management was shared with the participants. By prioritizing the health of our community, we ensure that the foundation for empowerment remains strong, as physical well-being is a fundamental prerequisite for anyone striving to lead a self-reliant and productive life.\n\nFurthermore, we conduct regular awareness sessions on topics like cyber security and digital ethics in collaboration with the NIIT Foundation. In an increasingly digital world, it is vital that our youth are not only technologically proficient but also aware of the risks and responsibilities that come with online engagement. These workshops cover themes like online safety, data protection, and password management, helping our trainees safeguard their digital presence. This focus on digital literacy as a tool for safety and empowerment is another way we prepare our students for the complexities of modern life.\n\nReflecting on the success of these outreach programs, we see a community that is more connected, creative, and empowered. These initiatives foster a sense of belonging and provide opportunities for self-expression that are often missing in marginalized neighborhoods. They also allow our volunteers and supporters to see the direct impact of their contributions. Moving forward, we plan to expand our outreach activities, reaching more children and families with even more diverse programs. At Saksham Bharti, we don\'t just train individuals; we build communities, and \'Ulaas\' is a shining example of how we bring light and hope to the lives we touch.\n\nBy engaging with schools and colleges through guest lectures, we also bridge the gap between classroom learning and real-world application. Our experts from fields like Retail, IT, and Fashion share their insights with students, inspiring them to pursue skill-based education. These interactions provide students with updated knowledge aligned with current industry trends and career opportunities. We believe that by reaching out and sharing our expertise, we can inspire a new generation to take charge of their future through skill development and lifelong learning. Our community outreach is not just about giving; it is about growing together.','frontend/assets/images/blog_summer_camp.png','2026-05-14 09:34:03'),(5,'Our Planet-Friendly Path: Embracing Clean Energy','Environmental sustainability is no longer a choice but a necessity, and at Saksham Bharti, we are committed to doing our part. As an organization dedicated to social good, we recognize that the well-being of our community is inextricably linked to the health of our planet. This year, we have made significant strides in our \'Planet-Friendly\' journey by embracing clean energy and implementing green practices across our operations. We believe that by integrating sustainability into our core activities, we are setting an example for our trainees and the community, fostering a culture of environmental responsibility and stewardship.\n\nThe highlight of our green initiatives is the successful installation of solar panel systems at our Vikas Nagar and Dwarka centers. These systems are now fully operational and provide a significant portion of the electricity needed to run our training programs and offices. By switching to solar energy, we are not only reducing our carbon footprint but also realizing substantial savings in our operational costs—funds that can now be redirected to further enhance our social impact and reach more people. The sight of solar panels on our rooftops is a powerful symbol of our commitment to a cleaner, greener future, and it serves as a practical lesson for our students on the importance of renewable energy and innovation.\n\nBeyond solar energy, every Saksham Bharti center prioritizes environmental awareness through various green activities and eco-impact initiatives. We regularly organize plantation drives where our staff and trainees come together to plant trees and maintain greenery in and around our facilities. These drives are more than just about planting; they are about connecting with nature and understanding the vital role trees play in our ecosystem and the fight against climate change. We also conduct eco-impact sessions for our trainees, where they learn about waste management, water conservation, and the broader impact of human activity on the environment.\n\nA key part of our environmental strategy is the implementation of better waste management practices within our centers. We encourage the reduction of single-use plastics and promote the recycling of materials wherever possible. In our Fashion Designing courses, trainees are taught how to repurpose fabric scraps and understand the principles of sustainable fashion. In our office operations, we are moving toward more digital processes to reduce paper consumption. These small but consistent steps help us reduce our environmental footprint and instill a sense of \'responsible consumption\' in our students, aligned with SDG Goal 12.\n\nOur commitment to sustainability also extends to our choice of partners and programs. We align our work with multiple United Nations Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs), including Goal 7 (Affordable and Clean Energy), Goal 12 (Responsible Consumption and Production), and Goal 13 (Climate Action). By focusing on these global targets, we ensure that our local actions contribute to a larger, more sustainable impact. We believe that education for sustainability is a vital part of vocational training, as it prepares our students to be conscious professionals who care about the impact of their work on the world around them.\n\nThe results of our planet-friendly approaches are already visible in the attitudes and actions of our trainees. They are more aware of environmental issues and are actively participating in our green initiatives, often bringing these practices back to their own homes and neighborhoods. We have seen a significant reduction in our reliance on conventional energy sources and a steady decrease in our waste generation. Moreover, our efforts have garnered appreciation from our partners and the community, reinforcing our position as a responsible and forward-thinking organization that cares about both people and the planet.\n\nFurthermore, we are exploring more \'green\' livelihood opportunities for our trainees. We believe that the emerging green economy will offer many new job roles, and we want to prepare our students to take advantage of these. Whether it is in renewable energy, sustainable agriculture, or eco-friendly manufacturing, we are looking at how we can adapt our curriculum to include the skills needed for these sectors. This forward-looking approach ensures that our trainees are not just job-ready for today but also for the sustainable economy of tomorrow. At Saksham Bharti, we believe in empowering youth for a future that is both prosperous and sustainable.\n\nLooking forward, we aim to make all our centers 100% solar-powered and further expand our environmental education programs. We want to collaborate with more environmental organizations and experts to bring in specialized knowledge and create even more impactful green initiatives. Our journey toward sustainability is an ongoing one, and we are committed to continuous improvement and innovation. We invite our supporters and the community to join us in this mission. Together, we can build a world where progress and sustainability go hand in hand, ensuring a healthy and prosperous planet for generations to come. Every step we take on this planet-friendly path is a step toward a better world for everyone.','frontend/assets/images/blog_solar_panels.png','2026-05-14 09:34:03');
